VW to Improve Computer Systems Against Hacker Attacks, FTD Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-08-25T02:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/vw-to-improve-computer-systems-against-hacker-attacks-ftd-says.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW)  will invest a “three-
digit million-euro amount” in its information technology
systems in coming years after an internal investigation found
that  Europe ’s largest automaker needs to improve its protection
against hacker attacks,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported
today, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
